flowchart LR
  classDef user fill:#EFF6FF,stroke:#2563EB,color:#1E3A8A,stroke-width:1px;
  classDef app fill:#FFF8F1,stroke:#F97316,color:#1A1A1A,stroke-width:1px;
  classDef data fill:#ECFDF5,stroke:#10B981,color:#064E3B,stroke-width:1px;
  classDef ext fill:#F3F4F6,stroke:#6B7280,color:#111827,stroke-width:1px;
  classDef note fill:#FEF3C7,stroke:#D97706,color:#7C2D12,stroke-width:1px;

  U[User]:::user --> UI[Gradio UI app main py]:::app
  PDF[PDF Upload]:::user --> UI
  Q[Question optional]:::user --> UI

  UI --> ORCH[Orchestration callbacks]:::app

  ORCH --> OCR[Step 1 OCR extract_text]:::app
  OCR --> OCR_API[mistral-ocr-latest]:::ext

  OCR --> TOPIC[Step 2 Topic classify]:::app
  TAX[data category_list txt]:::data --> TOPIC
  FTREF[data finetuned_model txt optional]:::data --> TOPIC
  TOPIC --> CHAT_API[mistral-large-latest or fine tuned]:::ext

  TOPIC --> QA[Step 3 QA optional]:::app
  QA --> CHAT_API

  ORCH --> OUT1[Outputs text topic answer]:::user

  ORCH --> EVAL[Evaluation mode single doc]:::app
  GT[Ground truth text topic answer]:::user --> EVAL
  EVAL --> METRICS[WER ROUGE-L TopicAcc]:::app
  EVAL --> JUDGE[LLM judge Topic Answer]:::app
  METRICS --> REPORT[Evaluation report]:::app
  JUDGE --> REPORT
  REPORT --> OUT2[KPIs latency tokens cost quality]:::user
  REPORT --> RES[results json]:::data

  subgraph OfflineLoop[Offline loop scripts]
    DL[scripts download_dataset py]:::app
    EV[scripts run_evaluation py]:::app
    INS[scripts inspect_topics py]:::app
    BUILD[scripts build_finetune_dataset py]:::app
    FT[scripts run_finetune py]:::app
    ENT[Fine tune entitlement required]:::note

    DL --> EV
    EV --> INS
    INS --> BUILD
    BUILD --> FT
    FT --> ENT
  end

  DATA[data jsonl and pdfs]:::data --> DL
  DATA --> EV
  EV --> RES
